---
// TODO: ConvertKit / Stibee / Buttondown 등 뉴스레터 서비스 연결 후 form action 교체
---

<section class="bg-surface border-y border-border mt-16">
  <div class="container-prose py-12 text-center">
    <h3 class="mb-3">매주 1편. AI 도구 큐레이션.</h3>
    <p class="text-muted mb-6">
      1인 기업·프리랜서를 위한 한국어 환경 기준. 무료.
    </p>
    <form
      class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-2 max-w-md mx-auto"
      onsubmit="event.preventDefault(); alert('뉴스레터 서비스 연결 필요 — Stibee/ConvertKit');"
    >
      <input
        type="email"
        name="email"
        placeholder="email@example.com"
        required
        class="flex-1 border border-border bg-bg rounded-md px-4 py-2 focus:outline-none focus:border-accent"
      />
      <button
        type="submit"
        class="bg-accent text-accent-fg rounded-md px-5 py-2 font-medium hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity"
      >
        구독하기
      </button>
    </form>
  </div>
</section>
